Beekeeper
A Beekeeper is an individual who produces honey and other related products, playing a crucial role in agriculture.

Agriculture
Agriculture encompasses the cultivation of crops and livestock for food production.

Honey Bees
Honey Bees are important pollinators, essential for agriculture.

Heart Disease
Heart disease is a serious health condition affecting the heart.

LightRAG
LightRAG is a retrieval-based system that combines graph-based indexing with large language models.

LLM
The LLM is used to extract entities and relationships from each chunk of text during the graph-based indexing phase.

Query
A query represents a user's question or request for information.

Answer
An answer is a response to a user's question or request.

Domain
A domain is a specific subject area or topic that LightRAG focuses on.

Metric
A metric is a quantitative measure of the performance of a system.

Chunk
The LLM extracts entities and relationships from each chunk of text during the graph-based indexing phase.
